title: Ep. #34 | Catching Up: ASC Hosts Special with Kevin Woo and Jamie Park
description:
Are you ready for this? Eric’s not ready for this.

This very special episode reunites the ultimate After School Club trio: Kevin Woo, Jamie Park, and Eric Nam!

Kevin, Jamie, and Eric discuss old memories as hosts of After School Club, compare pre-debut stories, and eradicate the rumors over who Kevin was dating. Warning: many, many laughs in this one.

Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.

Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios

Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !
